dcterms:creator: Kevin Chen
dcterms:description: A game environment used for training a Deep Q-Network (DQN) agent to navigate a bird through pipes while avoiding obstacles to earn points. The observation space consists of the position of the bird, and the action space includes moving the bird up or down.
dcterms:title: Flappy Bird

dcterms:description: A stock trading simulation environment designed to optimize trading decisions using deep reinforcement learning. The environment simulates stock trading with metrics such as cash balance, stock prices, and account value.
dcterms:title: Stock Trading Data
